      <abstract>
        <p>Roundup of recent advertising account changes (Advertising column) (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The May Department Stores Co., St. Louis, to Doner, Southfield, Mich., to handle its media planning and buying, which had been handled by the Glennon Company, St. Louis, and Janik &amp; Associates, Los Angeles. Spending was estimated at $100 million. Doner has handled the creative assignment for May since 1998.</p>
